description:
Did you know that studies show people are more willing to share online than in person?

We live in a digital world, where most of us connect with others online, especially now that we have experienced a global pandemic. Society is changing, with most people digitally connected and spending the majority of their time online.

God's mission will never be halted, it is now expanding digitally, and many people can be reached with a single click. Bringing the Gospel to people today can be done in a variety of ways, one of which is through the internet. How are we going to do that? How can we help find people online and communicate with them?

Watch the video to find out the answers to these questions and other things we need to remember in order to be effective digital missionaries and finish the work entrusted to us.


—----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
